@<row><b>SS0</b><tab><b>Awaiting orders</b><tab>Unit is reset to "manual" and only executes 
@commands explicitely given. This is also the default setting. </row>
@<row><b>SS1</b><tab><b>Aggressive</b><tab>This strategy can be selected for all military units
@but Aircrafts. An SS1 unit ferociously attacks every enemy unit it encounters. Priority hereby 
@is given to the occupation of towns. Units capable of using <b><a href="FE.htm">FI</a></b> 
