@<row><b>SW3</b><tab><b>Zealous</b><tab>For walking and sailing units only. An SS3 unit
@does not stray from its path, it will attack all units silly enough to block its movement path. Remember
@that only your own units and structures as well those from your allies allow your units to pass; 
@neutral or enemy units and structures therefore will be viciously and immediately attacked! 
@Be careful! Still, units from a "final ally" Empire are spared.</row>
