@like Construction Worker Gangs and Bulldozers. When an SS10 unit moves onto a square without roads,
@it will automatically execute an <b><a href="ST.htm">CR</a></b> (Construct Road). Combined with 
@a <b><a href="GZ.htm">GT</a></b> (Go To)-commands, you can keep your construction unit
@busy for an eternity. </row>
