@<hint>Use the <b><a href="GZ.htm">GT</a></b> command instead of  <b><a href="RE.htm">MV</a></b>, whenever the distance to travel exceeds three or more squares.</hint>
@<hint>The repeat command <b><a href="WI.htm">RP</a></b> can save a lot of space and
